OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783639966
OL,3,CDisability benefits not fit for
OL,4,Cpurpose and need bold reform, says Pip
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FDisability benefits are no longer fit
OL,8,Ffor purpose and are failing to keep
OL,9,Fpace with how health and work have
OL,10,Fchanged over the past decade, the
OL,11,FTimms Review has found.
OL,13,FThe review of the Personal
OL,14,FIndependence Payment (Pip), conducted
OL,15,Fby Sir Stephen Timms, the Minister for
OL,16,FSocial Security and Disability,
OL,17,Fpublished its interim report on
OL,18,FThursday, ahead of a full publication
OL,19,Fexpected later this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
