FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783639966
OL,3,CDisability benefits not fit for
OL,4,Cpurpose and need bold reform, says Pip
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FDrawing on findings from more than
OL,8,F38,000 responses, alongside workshops
OL,9,Fand engagement with disabled people,
OL,10,Ftheir organisations and experts, it is
OL,11,Fone of the largest co-produced reviews
OL,12,Fdelivered by the government.
OL,14,FThe ongoing assessment of the Pip
OL,15,Fsystem is the first full review of its
OL,16,Ffunction since the introduction of the
OL,17,Fpayments in 1993.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
