OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783639966
OL,3,CDisability benefits not fit for
OL,4,Cpurpose and need bold reform, says Pip
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThe Review launched last October to
OL,8,Fhelp support disabled people to
OL,9,Fachieve better health, higher living
OL,10,Fstandards and greater independence,
OL,11,Fincluding through employment.
OL,13,FThe final report, which will include
OL,14,Frecommendations for change, is due in
OL,15,Fautumn, and the Government has
OL,16,Finsisted the review will ensure Pip is
OL,17,F"fit and fair for the future".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
