OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783639966
OL,3,CDisability benefits not fit for
OL,4,Cpurpose and need bold reform, says Pip
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThe review team said their
OL,8,Frecommendations will be "bold in
OL,9,Fnature and bold in recognition of the
OL,10,Fwider environment in which disabled
OL,11,Fpeople in the UK are living".
OL,13,FAround 10 million working-age people
OL,14,Freport living with a disability `
OL,15,Fequivalent to 24% of the working-age
OL,16,Fpopulation, compared with under 17% in
OL,17,F2013/14. There have been greater
OL,18,Fincreases in the prevalence of
OL,19,Fdisability among young people and a
OL,20,Frise in mental health conditions.
OL,26,@pD@YOUsD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
