OL,3,CDisability benefits not fit for
OL,4,Cpurpose and need bold reform, says Pip
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"We are immensely grateful to the tens
OL,8,Fof thousands of people who have taken
OL,9,Fthe time to share their lived
OL,10,Fexperience and make a valuable
OL,11,Fcontribution to this Review.
OL,13,F"We've heard loud and clear: Pip is
OL,14,Fhighly valued as a benefit but is not
OL,15,Ffit for purpose. We are committed to
OL,16,Fmaking changes so that Pip can fulfil
OL,17,Fits purpose."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@MO]
